  Erdos-Faber-Lovasz Conjecture

  Domain: mathematics
  ID: opa.mathematics.graph-theory.erdos-faber-lovasz-conjecture
  Status: Open

  Take n complete graphs, each with n vertices. Combine them so that any two share at most one vertex. Then you can color the edges of each complete graph (equivalently, the vertices of the union) using just n colors, so that no two adjacent edges share a color.

-/

